title: We talk to an expert, Sharon McMahon, about how the election results will come in!
description: We don't get political on this morning show but we want to make sure everyone is informed on how the election results will come in!  We have an expert on, Sharon McMahon, to explain to all of us how and when the results will be set and what could happen if there are disputes about the results!
